  [ 73] getlocal 1 .............................. <obj2RectInfo>
  [ 75] getobjprop 110 .......................... <obj2RectInfo.edgeOffset>
  [ 77] add ..................................... <obj1Rect + obj2RectInfo.edgeOffset>
